This paper deals with parameter estimation in a communication system, specifically channel estimation using quantized observations. This falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the impact of hardware imperfections, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper mentions the use of analog-to-digital converters, which could fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
